37e3587b37f24372750066647ae7155fa8","tid":871931,"uid":103531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T00:17:18.000Z","msg":"我覺得似法國里昂車站追撞事故多d<br />\n法國單野係有人拉左emergency Barke，之後氣壓鎖死個個brake,車長為左個氣壓表回復正常，打開氣閥放氣，之後繼續行車，為左追時間而加速，但去到要減速嗰時先發現已經減唔到速，最後㩒左緊急制鎖曬所有軌道列車通訊，成列列車撞向喺里昂車站停靠中的列車。<br />\n<br />\n台鐵講話車長回報空氣壓縮機有問題，喺宜蘭停靠有technician 上車幫手，會唔會就係放曬d氣令車頭個表回復正常，之後再開車為左追時間就熄ATP加快（亦有機會係空氣壓縮機問題令ATP太多錯誤訊息而死機)，點知去到新馬站個彎位前就發現減唔到速，結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b8afe273f8ef0865d8b0f4fadffea701f6bf4e","tid":871931,"uid":124430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T01:17:22.000Z","msg":"我上個月先坐台鐵同一條線  班班車都delay 20分鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ef8e2f92d6528c5817f54b0fd54fe59ace2478","tid":871931,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T01:59:17.000Z","msg":"香港高鐵有冇安全帶"},{"pid":"c70a3bb96862c502173c78355339601035139dca","tid":871931,"uid":1672,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07b8afe273f8ef0865d8b0f4fadffea701f6bf4e","tid":871931,"uid":124430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T01:17:22.000Z","msg":"我上個月先坐台鐵同一條線  班班車都delay 20分鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:44:19.000Z","msg":"你應該坐出事嗰班吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814bd1bcd3d1479374a4f195441239bb287d429e","tid":871931,"uid":124430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c70a3bb96862c502173c78355339601035139dca","tid":871931,"uid":1672,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07b8afe273f8ef0865d8b0f4fadffea701f6bf4e","tid":871931,"uid":124430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T01:17:22.000Z","msg":"我上個月先坐台鐵同一條線  班班車都delay 20分鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:44:19.000Z","msg"